REQUIREMENTS:

  - Control Node
    Name   : control
    Type   : GUI or Minimal
    Disk 1 : 30 GB
    Disk 2 : 20 GB
    CPU    : 2 - 4 GB
    RAM    : 4
    IPv4   : 10.211.55.100

  - Managed Hosts
    Name   : server1, server2
    Type   : Minimal
    Disk 1 : 20 GB
    CPU    : 2
    RAM    : 4 GB
    IPv4   : 10.211.55.101-102


______________________________


INITIAL SETUP:
- Run 'scripts/requirements.sh'
- Run 'sudo setup.sh'


______________________________


Core Tasks:
- Break out tasks from main.yml to make the project more modular and manageable
- Re-evaluate variables and reorganize
- Utilize ansible-vault for user creation and other sensitive data


Playbook Tasks
- register_host_local.yml
- register_host_remote.yml


Playbook Breakout
- configure_repo_local.yml
- configure_user_ansible.yml
